    <h2 class="tech-heading fade-in delay-1">Features.</h2>

    <div class="fade-in delay-2">
      <h3 class="cs-h3">Image Geolocation</h3>
      <p class="cs-desc" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">EXIF geolocation data is extracted from uploaded images to automatically position map pins at the correct location, streamlining the spot-adding experience.</p>
      <div class="cs-img-block">
        <img src="/assets/spot-hub/spot-upload.gif" alt="Spot upload demonstration">
        <p class="cs-img-cap">Single spot upload with auto-geolocation</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="cs-h3">Batch Upload</h3>
      <p class="cs-desc" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Up to 50 images can be selected at once. Geolocation data automatically groups nearby images together. A drag-and-drop interface allows corrections before creating spots individually.</p>
      <div class="cs-img-block">
        <img src="/assets/spot-hub/batch-upload.gif" alt="Batch upload demonstration">
        <p class="cs-img-cap">Batch upload with automatic grouping</p>
      </div>

      <h3 class="cs-h3">AI Image Analysis (Gemini)</h3>
      <p class="cs-desc" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Google Gemini AI analyses spot images with a predefined prompt to generate suggested tags, enhancing the tagging process and improving discoverability.</p>
      <div class="cs-img-block">
        <img src="/assets/spot-hub/tag-suggestions.gif" alt="AI tag suggestions demonstration">
        <p class="cs-img-cap">Gemini-powered AI tag suggestions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

